ENTRIES1.title: Aon Risk Reward Challenge
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Season-long Aon Risk Reward Challenge will highlight the world’s best professional golfers

ENTRIES1.title: Kids Zone presented by the Dallas Mavericks
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Open Friday – Sunday of Tournament Week, come meet the mascot, get out on the sport court and experience all the fun with the Dallas Mavericks

ENTRIES1.title: Tailgate on the Green
ENTRIES1.subtitle: With free admission to all ticketed spectators, Tailgate on the Green, the largest tailgate on tour, is the place to enjoy the world’s best female golfers in addition to football, partner activations, Tribute Live and more!

ENTRIES1.title: Tribute Trail 5K presented by AT&T
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Saturday, October 5th in conjunction with tournament play, run through the golf course and the trails alongside Lake Lewisville in the inaugural Tribute Trail 5K presented by AT&T

ENTRIES1.title: Tribute Live!
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Ever wonder what it would be like to live on The Tribute peninsula? Come check out The Tribute: LIVE pavilion during the LPGA tournament for four full days of activities and programming for all ages!
